Remembrall is an application that allows users to:
1. Maintain day-to-day TO-DO-LIST
2. Sends notifications about the items in the TO-DO list

Notifications will be terminal notifications (desktop notifications to also be added).

A daemon process, that checks for items available in the TO-DO list,
shall run every n hours to display them.

Prototype architecture:
- Python script that allows CRUD of items of TO-DO list
- Daemon process that shall run ever n hours to display items
